sequenceDiagram
  participant F as Dashboard Feature
  participant G as Gateway
  participant AN as Analytics Service
  participant DB as Mongo analytics

  par Summary
    F->>G: GET /api/analytics/dashboard/summary
    G->>AN: summary query
    AN->>DB: findOne by userId
    DB-->>AN: analytics document
    AN-->>F: summary DTO
  and Reading Analytics
    F->>G: GET /api/analytics/dashboard/reading-analytics
    G->>AN: analytics query
    AN->>DB: findOne by userId
    AN-->>F: charts + stats
  and Goals
    F->>G: GET /api/analytics/dashboard/reading-goals
    G->>AN: goals query
    AN->>DB: findOne by userId
    AN-->>F: goals + completion
  and Activity
    F->>G: GET /api/analytics/dashboard/activity
    G->>AN: activity query
    AN->>DB: findOne by userId
    AN-->>F: activity timeline
  end
